<L>There Bennington's en&s;anguin'd plain,</L>
<L>And Stony-Point, the prize of Wayne.</L>
<L><PB N="74" REF="017750_0073_0FA26E2DDBDDD5B8">
Behold near Del'ware's icy roar,</L>
<L>Where morning dawns on Tre<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">on's &s;hore,</L>
<L>While He&s;&s;ians &s;pread their Chri&s;tmas <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word">,</L>
<L>Ru&s;h rude the&s;e uninvited gue&s;ts;</L>
<L>Nor aught avail, to Whigs a prize,</L>
<L>Their martial whi&s;kers gri&s;ly &s;ize.</L>
<L>On <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> plains our heroes yield,</L>
<L>And &s;pread in &s;light the vanqui&s;h'd field,</L>
